At the very least, then, a share of the booty will fall to the Dutch ship, and indeed a much larger share than to the British ship, just as the Dutch vessel is , herself much larger, and, as the leader, of much more consequence. bThen, tou, this law of war has been regarded as just from the remotest antiquity‚ namely, that they also should receive a share of the booty who have held the enemy in check, and that those who have , captured the booty should not hold all of it, since it was realized that the others too had played a part in securing it.
